Davis Product Line
Listed below you will see the various types of quality paint we have in our Davis Paint Line. Please click the corresponding number next to the product for specific product details.
If you are in need of MSDS or Technical Data Sheets, please click here.



Exterior Primers:



Hold-Tite Acrylic Latex House Paint Primer is a durable primer for exterior wood surfaces. This product dries in about 1 hour for topcoating with latex house paint to provide an all-latex painting system with outstanding blister and mildew resistance along with excellent color retention. This primer is intended for use on both new wood and previously painted wood in poor condition. It contains special resin which reacts with the stains from bleeding woods such as cedar, redwood, mahogany and fir plywood to prevent discoloration of the topcoat. When staining is severe, a second coat may be necessary to be certain the staining is blocked. This product features water clean-up. Brush application is recommended with this product, particularly on raw wood.

Da-Luxe Oil Primer White: Da-Luxe House Paint Primer is a premium quality pigmented, oil/alkyd primer for exterior use. Da-Luxe house Paint Primer is specially formulated for use under latex or oil base topcoats on unpainted wood, bleeding woods such as cedar, redwood or mahogany, or on previously painted weathered surfaces. It is designed for sealing porous surfaces and improving bond to chalky surfaces. This product may be applied by brush, roller or spray, however, brush is preferred.





Interior Primers: 



Kwic-Kote Wall Primer & Sealer is a fast drying, vinyl acrylic wall primer for interior walls and ceilings. Kwic-Kote is specially recommended for unpainted drywall surfaces as it will not raise the surface fibers. Kwic-Kote may also be used on new or previously painted plaster, masonry or tight wallpaper. This product may be topcoated with either latex or oil based finishes. Kwic-Kote features quick dry, easy water clean-up and application with brush, roller or spray.





Exterior House & Trim Finishes: 



Hold-Tite Flat Acrylic Latex House Paint is a premium quality flat latex house paint for wood and wood-based products, masonry, stucco, cement and cinder block, primed metal and all previously painted or stained surfaces. This product can be applied over properly prepared latex or oil based paint or primer. Hold-Tite Flat Acrylic Latex House Paint features water clean-up and rapid dry along with easy application with brush, roller or spray. This product offers high hiding and exceptional durability in a pleasant flat finish
Hold-Tite Flat Acrylic Latex House Paint is available in the following: Pastel Base (2400), Tint Base (2410), Deep Base (8495) and Accent Base (2499). Hold-Tite Flat is also available in the following ready-mix colors: (2401) Yuma Beige, (2413) Flagstone Gray, (2418) Palm Tan, (2431) Venetian Red, (2437) Clove Brown and (2438) Black.

Hold-Tite Satin Acrylic House & Trim Paint is a premium quality acrylic emulsion exterior coating. It has a satin finish and has a tough, flexible film that is unsurpassed. It provides a breathable film for excellent blister resistance. Hold-Tite Satin can be used on properly prepared, primed or previously painted wood siding, doors, sash, trim, shutters, shakes and shingles, stucco, brick, cement and cement block, aluminum siding, unglazed cement-asbestos shingles and siding. This product may also be used on primed or previously painted structural metal surfaces. Features water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller and spray.
Hold-Tite Satin is available in the following bases: Pastel Base (4050), Tint Base (4060), Deep Base (4065) and Accent Base (4099). Hold-Tite Satin also comes in 1 ready-mix color: (4053) Colonial Brown.

Hold-Tite Acrylic Semi-Gloss Latex House & Trim paint is a 100% Acrylic product specially formulated for both professional and do-it-yourself use. This unique product is recommended for properly prepared exterior surfaces of wood and wood based products, masonry, concrete block, stucco, metal and previously painted or stained surfaces. This product may be used with excellent results year round even down to temperatures of 35Â° F. This product features easy soap and water clean-up and may be applied via brush, roller or spray.
Hold-Tite Semi-Gloss is available in the following bases: Pastel Base (4150), Tint Base (4160), Deep Base (4165) and Accent Base (4199).

Davis Master Painter Professional Coatings (MPPC) 410 Flat Acrylic Latex House & Trim Paint is a high quaility, acrylic product specifically formulated for professional use. This unique product is recommended for properly primed/prepared exterior surfaces of wood and wood-based products, masonry, concrete block, stucco, metal and previously painted or stained surfaces. This product features water clean-up and easy application by brush, roller or spray.
Master Painter 410 Flat Acrylic Latex is available in the following bases: (4410) White Base, (4411) Pastel Base, (4412) Tint Base, (4419) Accent Base and (4413) Deep Base.

Davis Master Painter Professional Coatings (MPPC) 430 Satin Acrylic Latex House & Trim Paint is a high quality, acrylic product specifically formulated for professional use. This unique product is recommended for properly primed/prepared exterior surfaces or wood and wood-based products, masonry, concrete block, stucco, metal and previously painted or stained surfaces. This product features water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Davis Master Painter 430 Satin Acrylic Latex is available in the following bases: (4430) White Base, (4431) Pastel Base, (4432) Tint Base, (4439) Accent Base and (4433) Deep Base.






Interior Wall & Trim Finishes: 



Da-Tex Eggshell Wall Enamel Latex is a premium quality latex eggshell enamel for interior use. Da-Tex's finish, when viewed directly, appears to be without luster; however, when viewed from an angle it has a low sheen finish. The film has excellent resistance to repeated washing. Da-Tex Eggshell is unsurpassed for use on primed or previously painted wood or metal trim, doors and cabinets, as well as new or previously painted masonry, drywall and ceilings. Da-Tex Eggshell is highly recommended for offices, schools, apartments, motels, hospitals and nursing homes. Da-Tex Eggshell features quick dry, water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Da-Tex Eggshell is available in the following: Pastel Base (3150), Tint Base (3160), Deep Base (3165) and Accent Base (3199). 

Da-Tex Flat One Coat Vinyl Latex is a flat vinyl acrylic wall paint that is unmatched in quality and provides one-coat coverage, provided the surface is in good condition and the color change is not extreme. This product dries to a non-yellowing decorative finish and is known for its excellent washability. Da-Tex Flat excels on new or previously painted drywall, plaster, masonry walls and ceilings, as well as previously painted or primed wood and metal surfaces. This paint is self-priming on plaster, drywall and masonry surfaces and will not raise the fibers of drywall products. This product features quick dry, water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
This product is available in the following: Pastel Base (5555), Tint Base (8440), Deep Base (8445) and Accent Base (5599). 

Da-Tex Satin Enamel Latex Wall Paint is an interior satin vinyl acrylic latex enamel wall paint of the highest quality and performance where excellent washability is an important factor. This product is for use on primed or previously painted plaster, masonry, drywall and ceilings. Da-Tex Satin is also an excellent finish for primed or previously painted wood or metal surfaces. This product is especially suited for offices, apartments, schools, motels and nursing homes where a low oder is a must. Da-Tex Satin features quick dry, water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Da-Tex Satin Interior Enamel Wall Paint is available in the following: Pastel Base (5755), Tint Base (8423), Deep Base (8428) and Accent Base (5799). 
Da-Tex Satin Interior Enamel Wall Paint is available in 1 Gallon and 5 Gallon Containers.

Davis Master Painter Professional Coatings (MPPC) 310 Flat Acrylic Latex Wall Paint is a high quality, acrylic product specifically formulated for professional use. This unique product is recommended for interior applications on properly primed/prepared drywall, metal, plaster, wood, concrete block and other masonry surfaces. This product features water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Available in the following bases: (4313) Deep Base, (4319) Accent Base, (4311) pastel base and (4312) tint base.

Davis Master Painter Professional Coatings (MPPC) 330 Semi-Gloss Acrylic Latex Wall & Trim Enamel is a high quality, acrylic product specifically formulated for professional use. This unique product is recommended for interior applications only on properly primed/prepared drywall, metal, plaster, wood, concrete block and other masonry surfaces. This product features water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Available in the following bases: (4333) Deep Base, (4339) Accent Base, (4331) pastel base and (4332) tint base

Da-Tex Alkyd Semi-Lustre is a superior quality, low lustre alkyd enamel designed for interior and exterior usage. Da-Tex Alkyd has a good non-penetrating quality that presents a uniform finish. This product provides excellent hiding and produces an attractive hand-rubbed finish. Da-Tex Alkyd is unsurpassed for is washability. This product is exceptional for use on primed or previously painted wood or metal trim, doors, cabinets, plaster, masonry and wallboard walls and ceilings. Da-Tex Alkyd is ideal for rooms and corridors where a high durable, non-glare finish is desired. This product features easy application with brush, roller or spray. MPI#94 Approved





Ceiling Paint:



Da-Tex Ceiling Paint Latex Flat White is a premium quality vinyl acrylic flat finish which is unsurpassed in quality and provides one-coat coverage, provided the surface is in good condition and color change is not extreme. It dries to a non-yellowing decorative finish. This product excels on new or previously painted drywall, plaster or masonry ceilings as well as previously painted or primed wood and metal surfaces. It is self-priming on plaster, drywall and masonry surfaces and will not raise the fibers of drywall products. Product features a quick-dry formula, water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.

Davis MPPC (Master Painter Professional Coatings) 305 Flat Latex Ceiling Paint is an economical interior vinyl acrylic latex paint specifically formulated for professional use on properly primed/prepared ceilings. This product features water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.





All Purpose Enamels:



Ever-Bright Alkyd High Gloss Rust Inhibitive Enamel is a high gloss, fast drying, rust inhibitive enamel for use on interior and exterior applications. Ever-Bright is unsurpassed for use on primed or previously painted surfaces such as wood, metal, plaster, drywall, machinery, storage tanks and all other types of wood and metal. Interior surfaces such as bathrooms and kitchens are given the most washable surface when Ever-Bright is used. This product is lightfast and resists gasoline, grease, oil and water. Ever-Bright Enamel features easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Davis Ever-Bright Enamel is available in the following: White Base (5800), Tint Base (5850), Deep Base (5855) and Accent Base (5899). Ever-Bright is also available in the following factory tint colors: Liberty Blue (5842), Black (5844), Emerald Green (5849), Earth Brown (5882) and Yellow (5896). All of the above products are MPI #9 APPROVED
(0635) Aluminum is MPI#1 APPROVED

Davis Master Painter High Performance Acrylic Gloss Latex Enamel is a high quality acrylic product specifically formulated for both the professional and the do-it-yourself user. This high-performance enamel may be used on a variety of interior or exterior, previously painted or primed wood, metal or masonry surfaces. Use on interior walls, doors, cabinets, woodwork, trim, knick-knacks and toys; or use on exterior trim, doors, shutters, windows and railings. This product features water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.





Floor Finishes:



Supr-Tuff Porch & Floor Oil is a traditional solvent thinned alkyd, highly durable, mar-resistant gloss, porch and floor enamel designed for interior and exterior use. Supr-Tuff is formulated for use on new or previously painted floors and/or stairs constructed of wood, metal and aged concrete. Supr-Tuff is capable of withstanding frequent scrubbings. This product features quick dry to a tile-like, elastic finish and may be applied by brush, roller or spray.
Supr-Tuff is available in the following colors: White, Tile Red, and Silver Gray. If you are looking for a custom color, we do have this in a tint base to get custom color you want!

Davis Wondr-Tuff Latex Porch & Floor Enamel is a premium quality, quick drying satin finish latex floor paint. Wondr-Tuff is especially suited for use on unpainted, etched interior or exterior concrete (new or old) and previously painted or primed wood. This product is ideal for use on basement floors, steps, porches, factory and warehouse flooring. Wondr-Tuff has excellent abrasion resistance and will withstand the severe abuse and weathering encountered both in and out of doors. Wondr-Tuff features quick dry, water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
Davis Wondr-Tuff Porch & Floor Enamel is available in the following colors: White (5650), Red (5657), Green (5659) and Silver Gray (5661).
Davis Wondr-Tuff is available in 1 Gallon Containers Only.





Exterior Wood Stain:



Eli Weatherby'sÂ® Rustic Oil Stain is a decorative and durable semi-transparent stain primarily for use on rough sawn board, decks, fences, plywood and other similiar exterior wood surfaces. This product protects wood without hiding the natural texture and grain beauty. It is ideal for any type of clean and dry natural lumber, plywood or pressure-treated wood. Eli Weatherby'sÂ® Semi-Transparent Rustic Stain contains a special additive to provide maximum water repellence, which blocks moisture, helping to retard warping, cracking and peeling. Mildewcides are also incorporated to inhibit mildew growth.
Eli Weatherby'sÂ® Rustic Oil Stain is available in the following: Clear (0915), Cedar (0911), Redwood (0912) and Teak (0914).
Product may also be tinted to a variety of colors from the Rustic Stain Color Card. Cape Cod Gray, Espresso, Tobacco, Weathered Wood, Elm Leaf, Split Rail, Russet, Black Walnut and Mahogany






Interior Natural Wood Finishes:



Eventone Interior Wood Stain  was developed to penetrate deeply and beautifully color trim, floors, cabinets, paneling, doors and all other unfinished interior wood surfaces. This unique formula enhances the rich color of fine hardwoods or the natural beauty of soft woods without hiding the original grain. Eventone Interior Wood Stain will not fade or bleed.
Eventone Interior Wood Stain is available in the following:

0901 - Clear Stain Base
0941 - Oak
0942 - Cherrywood
0943 - Fruitwood
0945 - Provincial
0946 - Walnut
0947 - Dark Walnut

If you have a stain color you would like matched, bring it to our Service Center and let them take care of all of your stain needs!
All colors are Custom Tinted.

Da-Tex Flat One Coat Vinyl Latex is a flat vinyl acrylic wall paint that is unmatched in quality and provides one-coat coverage, provided the surface is in good condition and the color change is not extreme. This product dries to a non-yellowing decorative finish and is known for its excellent washability. Da-Tex Flat excels on new or previously painted drywall, plaster, masonry walls and ceilings, as well as previously painted or primed wood and metal surfaces. This paint is self-priming on plaster, drywall and masonry surfaces and will not raise the fibers of drywall products. This product features quick dry, water clean-up and easy application with brush, roller or spray.
This product is available in the following: Pastel Base (5555), Tint Base (8440), Deep Base (8445) and Accent Base (5599). This product is also made in a factory direct tint of Off-White (5597).


















