Â PRACTICE FOCUS AND EXPERIENCE

Robert Kaitz practices in the Employment and Litigation areas. Robert is a trial lawyer focusing primarily on employment, professional liability, and business litigation matters, as well as employment counseling.  Prior to joining Davis Malm, Robert was an associate at Boyle, Shaughnessy & Campo, P.C.Â  He also served as Law Clerk to the Honorable Judith Fabricant and the Honorable Peter Lauriat, both in the Suffolk County Superior Courtâs Business Litigation Session.
